CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 1, 1956, pg. 20, reads: "Ammon Aqua Show - Pictured are some of he participants in Aqua Show held at Ammon Pool. Left photo shows, left to right, Ida Goins, Brenda Stephens, Mary Hilliard and Otis Johnson, director..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Ida Goins wearing dark bathing suit on left, Brenda Stephens wearing Native American style costume, Mary Hilliard, and Ammon Center director Otis Johnson wearing pith helmet and Department of Parks and Recreation t-shirt, posed in front of chain link fence with bunting, at Ammon Recreation Center, Hill District
